headline: 2 Reasons to Like WAB and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Although Wabtec (currently trading at $203.18 per share) has gained 25.9% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 33.2% return during that period. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
